      "date": "2018-02-27 18:17:00.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: Code-Review-1\n\n(1 comment)\n\noverall this looks more like a debug patch material than something suitable for landing to master, no?\n\nThis probably could be further enhanced to better handle all these cases.",
