      },
      "date": "2018-02-27 18:41:29.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\n(1 comment)\n\nSince this problem has been seen in the field, I don't mind to land this as a debug patch, that also avoids crashing the node.  However, it should at least dump the stack (ratelimited) with a mention of LU-10669 so that we learn the callpath and users will hopefully update the ticket, and any other information that may be useful to debug this problem, so that if it is hit again we can make some progress.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 1
    },
